1. Create virtual env
py -3 -m venv [virtual env name]
py -3 -m venv .venv

2. Activate virtual env
.venv\scripts\activate

3. Install library:
python -m pip --cert [certification_path] --proxy [proxy] install numpy
e.g python -m pip --cert C:\ProgramData\cert\CA.cert --proxy http://proxy.com:8080 install numpy

4. Deactivate virtual env
deactivate
